    <briefdescription>
<para>A structure containing callbacks for input controller events. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The final parameter to all the callbacks is a void *, which will point to whatever payload data the user provides in MLInputSetControllerCallbacksEx. Individual callbacks which are not required by the client can be NULL.</para>
<para>This structure must be initialized by calling <ref refid="group___input_1gaf8c43f4ba01939f31180fd0ee488bc6b" kindref="member">MLInputControllerCallbacksExInit()</ref> before use.</para>
